{
  "name": "suggest_place",
  "agents": ["suggest_place_researcher", "suggest_place_composer"],
  "tasks": [
    {
      "name": "research_extra_place_task",
      "description": "Research ONE additional place to append to an existing day — do not redesign the day.\n\nContext:\n- overnight_city: {overnight_city}\n- day_index: {day_index}\n- date: {date} (weekday matters for closed_weekdays: Mon=0..Sun=6)\n- preferences: {preferences}\n- interests: {interests}\n- food_crawl_mode: {food_crawl_mode}\n- prefer_non_food: {prefer_non_food} (min_non_food_places={min_non_food_places})\n- energy_level: {energy_level}\n- remaining_minutes (hard budget for activity + travel of the new stop only): {remaining_minutes}\n- already_visited (forbidden place_keys / duplicates): {already_visited}\n- current_places_json (existing stops — complement these; do not repeat): {current_places_json}\n\nSearch for real named POIs in {overnight_city} — restaurants, shops, museums, attractions, facilities — not neighborhoods, wards, districts, or vague areas. If an area comes up, pick a concrete venue inside it. Every candidate needs a specific venue name and street-level address.\n\nWhen prefer_non_food=true (day still has zero non-food stops and food_crawl_mode=false), prioritize museum / park / shrine / shopping / cultural POI candidates — do not propose another restaurant.\n\nFor each candidate gather:\n- name, street-level address, maps/website when known\n- category and why it fits prefs/interests\n- estimated visit minutes AND likely travel_minutes_from_previous from the last current stop\n- operational_status (open|closed|unknown) — skip permanently closed\n- closed_weekdays and open_hours when the source states them\n\nPrefer candidates whose visit+travel clearly fits under remaining_minutes, and that add variety (different category or a different named venue than current_places_json — not a neighborhood name).\n\nReturn 2–4 candidates with evidence notes. No full DayPlan.",
      "expected_output": "A brief listing 2–4 open (or unknown) named POI candidates (not areas) with street addresses, hours/status, minutes, and why each complements the current day (non-food when prefer_non_food=true).",
      "agent": "suggest_place_researcher"
    },
    {
      "name": "compose_suggested_place_task",
      "description": "Pick exactly ONE Place from the research brief to append.\n\nHard rules (API will reject violations):\n- Not already visited (full forbidden list was applied in research — never pick an excluded key)\n- operational_status must not be \"closed\" (prefer \"open\"; use \"unknown\" only if research truly lacks status)\n- If closed_weekdays is known, it must not include the weekday of {date}\n- estimated_minutes + travel_minutes_from_previous MUST be <= {remaining_minutes} (leave a little slack if unsure)\n- order_in_day must be {next_order_in_day}\n- place_key required (stable slug from name|address)\n- Do not invent venues, hours, or status — only what the brief supports\n- When prefer_non_food={prefer_non_food} is true, category MUST NOT be food — pick a museum/park/shrine/shopping/cultural POI\n\nFill: specific venue name (not a neighborhood), street-level address (required), category, reason_to_visit, details, estimated_minutes (>0), travel_minutes_from_previous, order_in_day, place_key, operational_status, closed_weekdays, open_hours when known, maps_url/website_url when known, has_bathroom if known\n\nPrefer a stop that fits the preferences/interests already applied in research, and that complements current_places_json.\n\nOutput structured Place only — no Markdown essay.",
      "expected_output": "One named POI Place (street address; not an area) that is open (or unknown), not already visited, fits remaining_minutes, and is non-food when prefer_non_food=true.",
      "agent": "suggest_place_composer",
      "context": ["research_extra_place_task"],
      "output_pydantic": { "python": "suggest_models.Place" }
    }
  ],
  "process": "sequential",
  "verbose": true,
  "memory": false,
  "output_log_file": "logs/crew.log",
  "stream": false,
  "tracing": true,
  "inputs": {
    "overnight_city": "Tokyo",
    "day_index": "1",
    "date": "2026-09-01",
    "preferences": "culture, food, moderate pace",
    "interests": "temples, food",
    "food_crawl_mode": "false",
    "prefer_non_food": "false",
    "min_non_food_places": "1",
    "energy_level": "3",
    "remaining_minutes": "120",
    "already_visited": "",
    "current_places_json": "[]",
    "next_order_in_day": "4"
  }
}
